    "body": "The guts of this feature is implementing support for globing over filenames in a package and/or the global filesystem namespace.\n\nI didn't find it too hard to mock up an implementation using regexes, but I gave up when I realized that it would need to hack around our horrible inconsistent `Folder` implementation (`.Contents` does not recurse subdirectories, so `.Contents.Contains(foo)` can be false while `.Contains(foo)` is true).\n"
